Metadata.name: Fem Messiah (PSP)
Metadata.author: A Mudkip, Dexxtrip
Metadata.description:
A female messiah model with hair physics.
Includes both a portrait edit and the actual model with custom anims that have hair physics.
I was going to add coffins, but they broke and honestly it kind of makes sense that femc's Messiah wouldn't have them.
